{"tid":475537,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"同買東江水 香港價錢貴過深圳東莞7倍","createTime":"2017-11-21T08:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T09:53:56.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dbb227b0eabeb1807356d9b48f4be951e87d9452","tid":475537,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171121/large/1511247600_9dd2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171121%2Flarge%2F1511247600_9dd2.png&h=42b7865e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同樣買東江水，廣東省城市如東莞、深圳等，去年買水價格維持在每立方米不足1元，但香港去年實際每立方米水價高達7元，相差近7倍。即使廣東省在去年8月1日起，調整東深供水工程東莞至深圳沿線供水價格，供深圳水庫的價格從每立方米人民幣0.945元增至1.07元（折合港幣1.28元），深圳水價仍較香港便宜得多。<br />\n<br />\n去年本港購買東江水費用44.92億港元，實際用水量僅6.29億立方米，平均每立方米水價高達7.14元。根據粵海投資年報，同年東莞、深圳水費11.64億元，用水量11.97億立方米，平均每立方米水價0.97元，與香港水價差距約7倍。<br />\n<br />\n過去10年香港購買東江水價格每年均上升，而深圳水費自2011年起凍結，根據《深圳晚報》報道，自2016年8月1日起，廣東省調整東深供水工程東莞至深圳沿線供水價格，供深圳水庫的價格從每立方米0.945元人民幣提高到1.07元（折合港幣1.28元），加幅達13%。而深圳自來水綜合價格統一調整至每立方米3.449元人民幣(折合港幣5.34元)，增幅約14.81%。<br />\n<br />\n香港購買東江水價格高昂，但水費凍結多年，現時首12立方米的用水量是免費，其後31立方米每一立方米的收費是4.16元，較深圳水費更便宜，到第三級收費每立方米才徵收6.45元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171121/57485403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F57485403&d=mg95djlf9FHQSCc7LfRtz3adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=9037a0f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F57485403&h=9ad1bd94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171121/57485403</a>"},{"pid":"e4d1da20741f6b8d9aa861141cc795775957be26","tid":475537,"uid":48112,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:14:47.000Z","msg":"出口比其他國家梗係貴啲"},{"pid":"592a7e8ade4c6b4c52f25b53a2e0f5ec31a3a6f8","tid":475537,"uid":15823,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:19:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出口比其他國家梗係貴啲</blockquote><br />\n賣家帶頭搞港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6428b6b5de3e9cdd707e450f545cdb7a78d0f3c9","tid":475537,"uid":48112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:07:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出口比其他國家梗係貴啲</blockquote><br />\n賣家帶頭搞港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6a3f663d8f41aa0f73a9f3b9db7f4f1372ffa1","tid":475537,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T09:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}